   "source": [
    "The quantities **x** and **y** are proportional.\n",
    "\n",
    "| x  | y  |\n",
    "|----|----|\n",
    "| 12 | 36 |\n",
    "| 18 | 54 |\n",
    "| 25 | 75 |\n",
    "\n",
    "Find the **constant of proportionality** *(r)* in the equation:\n",
    "\n",
    "\\[\n",
    "y = rx\n",
    "\\]\n",
    "\n",
    "**r =**\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "ced5b20a",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "3.0\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "x = [12, 18, 25]\n",
    "y = [36, 54, 75]\n",
    "\n",
    "r = y[0] / x[0]\n",
    "print(r)"
   ]
  }
 ],
